              Now 0 < p ** k                           by PRIME_POS, EXP_POS
               so q = p ** d * nq                      by MULT_LEFT_CANCEL, MULT_ASSOC, p ** k <> 0
              But p divides p ** d                     by prime_divides_self_power, 0 < d
              and p ** d divides q                     by divides_def, MULT_COMM
              ==> p divides q                          by DIVIDES_TRANS
